{"tid":1489674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"肯做正經野未？「又有手足俾人斬阿」","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:39:56.000Z","uid":229677,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"59a55ebef0837d1090b166b6854d41f334941e9b","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:29:59.000Z","msg":"我屌撚晒一眾連登狗公！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母隻假奶犬露果小小成班好似未撚見過女咁！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以專注返場運動阿！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你地對唔對得住幾位烈士既英靈？對唔對得住眼都冇埋失去光明既手足阿手？對唔對得住俾狗拉左入狗屋打到骨都斷埋既手足阿！？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家要做既係定死線升級阿</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾人轉移視線阿"},{"pid":"01f11f510f33934cc4f585574cd48db67670cdab","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f509318004664d2fb57199b07b3f07f40f974298","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64ced5612cbfe8eb11ea0962eeb2558001987f1d","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"464d07804fef1cbcfd1b78e0232489854cbb3b68","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:30:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffbb62bcb542ef6347ca75cf14a4e4ce2004165e","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b1a845c802c0458a1feed8cc67b1f7af3553614","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:31:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3225f7376fbab575a03b17c318e487f5d2afee43","tid":1489674,"uid":229677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"531573f6